{"tid":157481,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"街拍劣影求屌","createTime":"2017-03-15T14:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T11:31:46.000Z","uid":26845,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92b592109afb0e2c926bf57f5091be2103ae00f6","tid":157481,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/970Umdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F970Umdz.jpg&h=2ff27109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔算經常街拍 但呢張已經係呢年自己影得最好個張<br />\n80d+T70-300影 平時vsco+lightroom執相<br />\n想請教urban既相應該點執<br />\n希望有大師不吝賜教"},{"pid":"92465577a28a647e70638a64d8d036bf37128518","tid":157481,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"64ea37e47c7d37725af6d7e01b99f1c014ac4426","tid":157481,"uid":76554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"路過留個正評支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3d5decc65d0c47c1bb9d7989a32476030bfb4a","tid":157481,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"支持x2係咪用開呢個焦距？"},{"pid":"e75d1f315d06365fb9808854f7fbb090405f224f","tid":157481,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持x2係咪用開呢個焦距？</blockquote><br />\n平時差唔多全部用50/1.8影 係個日去海旁同公園先轉70300影"},{"pid":"b873b3d61bd7d6e0565818bc30f4058756a50d8f","tid":157481,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持x2係咪用開呢個焦距？</blockquote><br />\n平時差唔多全部用50/1.8影 係個日去海旁同公園先轉70300影</blockquote><br />\n50影人街拍會唔會難啲？"},{"pid":"1bac5c0dc20fc7e10e1e98252fa3d613fd0599d5","tid":157481,"uid":69792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"直線自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"ht