{"pid":"ff46e5527f71dcb4ae5305c7aea45d93e056ded9","tid":157481,"uid":69792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實街拍無話要特別點tune, 不過我自己喜好用黑白</blockquote><br />\n黑白好正 但係我鐘意冷色既街拍 所以想學點tone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前唔記得喺邊down過一啲攝影師lightroom嘅preset，雖然我覺得唔係咁啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過可以參考下"},{"pid":"5141231c59ae3731a94e617a9d6d34bb4cc47b15","tid":157481,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支持x2係咪用開呢個焦距？</blockquote><br />\n平時差唔多全部用50/1.8影 係個日去海旁同公園先轉70300影</blockquote><br />\n50影人街拍會唔會難啲？</blockquote><br />\n會 係夜晚同影廣角少少先會用 因為我影開夜景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇stm，80d拍片都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539bc47d0d6f261db4d0330e1635187961e28d16","tid":157481,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實街拍無話要特別點tune, 不過我自己喜好用黑白</blockquote><br />\n黑白好正 但係我鐘意冷色既街拍 所以想學點tone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係你想TONE到變日系?<br />\n<br />\n唔好系我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇研究過咩系咩系"},{"pid":"9f8b4e07f0ad7522911fc83facc6dec70d60f21e","tid":157481,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支持x2係咪用開呢個焦距？</blockquote><br />\n平時差唔多全部用50/1.8影 係個日去海旁同公園先轉70300影</blockquote><br />\n50影人街拍會唔會難啲？</blockquote><br />\n會 係夜晚同影廣角少少先會用 因為我影開夜景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇stm，80d拍片都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有試過 的確好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f721579c246e4029b2d92f12f59ce907e3fca341","tid":157481,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:12:09.000Z","msg":"有冇大師過兩招黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0351ab78dc69c24fdd97373c8de2078f33c217","tid":157481,"uid":12176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"覺得幾普通 冇咩可以評<br />\n另外你指冷色系街拍即係點？<br />\nshare下, 睇下我有冇磚可以拋"},{"pid":"9f8c33b154baae65499d4b9a5a96699bb30afa32","tid":157481,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T02:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得幾普通 冇咩可以評<br />\n另外你指冷色系街拍即係點？<br />\nshare下, 睇下我有冇磚可以拋</blockquote><br />\n唔敢擺人地啲相出黎<br />\n大約就係偏暗偏藍 又可以執到啲燈光好靚咁"},{"pid":"5a70de88c283a739d42bdf463299133cbd25b9e2","tid":157481,"uid":42624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"純個人意見<br />\n我覺得街拍個故事性好緊要 冇故事性都可以玩下對比/layer /幽默感，色調點tune都改變唔到張相嘅本質<br />\nAlex webb, matt stuart <br />\n呢兩個係自己幾鐘意嘅攝影師 樓主可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a51f70bd9e1a2ef6feb1fc360a27cb742da74c3","tid":157481,"uid":86623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直線自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/222703_2bbdad2672dcfd48f3615ac7cb4b406f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F222703_2bbdad2672dcfd48f3615ac7cb4b406f.jpg&h=eb218c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nD7100<br />\nSigma 17-50 f/2.8<br />\nISO 100<br />\n快門 1/100<br />\n光圈 f/5.6<br />\n<br />\n而家開始多用35mm</blockquote><br />\n我都幾鍾意呢種構圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/171809_71cd509c91e6c45434f63cbe9f6eedbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F171809_71cd509c91e6c45434f63cbe9f6eedbf.jpg&h=911add6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ht9J0p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fht9J0p7.jpg&h=3a4865a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRicoh GR II"},{"pid":"fdcf7c4a3f63e01b3f06cce068e6879762b93dba","tid":157481,"uid":69792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得幾普通 冇咩可以評<br />\n另外你指冷色系街拍即係點？<br />\nshare下, 睇下我有冇磚可以拋</blockquote><br />\n唔敢擺人地啲相出黎<br />\n大約就係偏暗偏藍 又可以執到啲燈光好靚咁</blockquote><br />\n唔知算唔算日系，偏冷色、低對比<br />\n攝於築地本願寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/180936_548f48ffb5dafd83bb8234fef49d3a77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F180936_548f48ffb5dafd83bb8234fef49d3a77.jpg&h=1ffa23a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ced43b4fd4dd5f4b9e7c9ec1b6e10d73b1de56b6","tid":157481,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔好整咁大暗角張相都靚先啦"},{"pid":"13d30fb50aaab6cad6a0f2a05ef0d6968b6eba61","tid":157481,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得幾普通 冇咩可以評<br />\n另外你指冷色系街拍即係點？<br />\nshare下, 睇下我有冇磚可以拋</blockquote><br />\n唔敢擺人地啲相出黎<br />\n大約就係偏暗偏藍 又可以執到啲燈光好靚咁</blockquote><br />\n唔知算唔算日系，偏冷色、低對比<br />\n攝於築地本願寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/180936_548f48ffb5dafd83bb8234fef49d3a77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F180936_548f48ffb5dafd83bb8234fef49d3a77.jpg&h=1ffa23a5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢張好，有臨場感， 打機角度"}]}